: netcom.com
: cd /pub/bbosen/Enigma/PC-LanSafe

: and get what's there. This is _crippled_ in that the cryptoalgorithms
: are all replaced with a ridiculously weak character substitution
: algorithm, but otherwise corresponds with our commercial software
: so you can test it for compatibility and ease of administration.

